import Input from "./Input";

const Form = () => {
  return (
    <form className="ip-form container">
      <Input
        inputLabel="Nome"
        inputType="text"
        inputInfo="name"
      />

      <Input
        inputLabel="ProfissÃ£o"
        inputType="text"
        inputInfo="job"
      />
      <Input
        inputLabel="Celular"
        inputType="number"
        inputInfo="phone-number"
      />

      <Input
        inputLabel="Meu IP"
        inputType="number"
        inputInfo="ip-address"
      />
    </form>
  );
};

export default Form;
